The Story behind 5th Element
A Modern Take on Timeless Indian Flavors
At 5th Element, we’re a team of passionate people brought together by one goal — to serve Indian cuisine that’s rich in tradition, yet fresh in approach.
Founded by restaurateur Sridhar Sannala, 5th Element is born out of a deep love for India’s diverse food culture. What started as a simple idea has grown into a bold vision: to elevate Indian cuisine and present it with pride on a global table.
Our kitchen blends old-world recipes with modern techniques, honoring the classics while introducing creative new dishes. From street-style favorites to refined regional specialties, every plate tells a story.
Whether you’re here for a family meal, a business lunch, or a special celebration, 5th Element offers a vibrant dining experience that feels both familiar and exciting.
"It’s not just a restaurant -
It's a place to
Connect.
Share.
Enjoy Good Food.
Come & Experience The 5th Element"
Our Journey so far..
2008 | The Grand Beginning
We opened the first 5th Element in Jacksonville’s Baymeadows, aiming to bring authentic Indian flavors to a wider audience
2019 | Sanford, FL
By 2019, a new location was established in Sanford, Florida, expanding the brand’s presence in the state.
2022 | Expansion to a few more places
The Palm Coast, Pompano & Daytona Beach branches were operational by 2022, serving the South Florida region with their diverse menu.
2024 | The Journey  Continues
With the growing demand for fresh Indian Cuisine in South Florida, we opened in Delray Beach & new branch in Jacksonville (Town Center).

Our Amenities
Each 5th Element location is designed for comfort and convenience. From spacious seating and easy parking to online ordering, third-party delivery, and inclusive menu options like vegan, gluten-free, and Halal—we make every visit smooth, satisfying, and enjoyable. Catering services are also available for events of all sizes.
